es and spreads under the knorr hellmann’s bango robertson’s and kissan brands the home care segment provides home care products such as powders liquids and capsules soap bars and various cleaning products under the dirt is good surf comfort sunlight domestos pureit and radiant brands the refreshment segment offers ice cream and teabased beverages under the heartbrand magnum lipton ben  jerry’s breyers and pg tips brands as well as operates t stores the company was formerly known as margarine unie nv and changed its name to unilever nv in  unilever nv was founded in  and is headquartered in rotterdam the netherlands unilever nv is a subsidiary of the unilever group details nameunilever nv tickerun exchangenyse founded market cap€ million websitehttpwwwunilevernl listings map weena  rotterdam  dk netherlands number of employees street current staff  unilever nv employees industry industrypersonal products sectorhousehold and personal products about company plans   simply wall st news   learning center help center   sitemap terms and conditions privacy policy related companies unilever lseulvr estée lauder companies nyseel coty nysecoty herbalife nysehlf edgewell personal care nyseepc nu skin enterprises nysenus avon products nyseavp usana health sciences nyseusna blackmores asxbkl inter parfums nasdaqgsipar related industries household products personal products   simply wall street pty ltd community design  us design patent  european design registration  standard  poor’s financial services llc all rights reserved this website contains factual information only rgb and not general or personal advice it does not take into account your investment objectives financial situation or needs you should seek independent financial and legal advice to consider if an investment is appropriate for your personal circumstances copyright   standard  poor’s financial services llc reproduction of sp capital iq in any form is prohibited except with the prior written permission of sp sp d